<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Student Experience</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <style>
    .experience-images {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .experience-images img {
      width: calc(50% - 10px);
      max-width: 600px;
      height: 350px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .experience-images img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .experience-images img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 220px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .experience-images img {
        height: 180px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="content">
  <h1>Student Experience</h1>
  <hr>
  <p>
    The student experience at our Academy is designed to be structured, supportive, and globally oriented, ensuring that learners receive both strong academic grounding and meaningful practical exposure throughout their training journey.

    From the moment of enrolment, students gain access to a secure online learning portal, which serves as the central hub for lectures, learning materials, assessments, progress tracking, and academic communication. This platform allows students to learn at a consistent pace while engaging with faculty through live virtual classroom sessions, interactive discussions, and guided coursework.

    The online theory phase emphasizes clarity of concepts, clinical relevance, and professional standards. Students progress through clearly defined modules, each supported by assignments, assessments, and feedback. Continuous evaluation helps students build confidence and ensures readiness before moving to the next stage of learning.

    As students advance, the experience transitions from academic learning to hands-on practical training. This phase provides supervised exposure to real-world clinical environments, allowing students to apply theoretical knowledge in a controlled and ethical manner. Practical training focuses on skill development, professional conduct, patient safety, and documentation practices.

    Throughout the program, students are encouraged to maintain a log book, recording learning outcomes, competencies achieved, and practical experiences. This structured documentation supports reflective learning and professional growth.

    The Academy also emphasizes international exposure and professional preparedness. Students receive guidance on global best practices, external certification pathways, and career awareness, helping them understand industry expectations while maintaining compliance with regulatory standards.

    Assessments, coursework, and evaluations are integrated throughout the program to ensure consistent engagement and academic integrity. Faculty and academic coordinators provide ongoing support, helping students stay on track and successfully complete each phase of the course.

    Overall, the student experience is designed to be progressive, immersive, and outcome-focused, supporting learners from foundational theory through practical training and course completion, while fostering professionalism, responsibility, and lifelong learning.
  </p>

  <!-- IMAGES BELOW TEXT -->
  <div class="experience-images">
    <img src="/images/image1.jpg" alt="Medical Training">
    <img src="/images/image2.jpg" alt="Student Experience">
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>